snippet.textDisplay:
As a 90s kid, I've witnessed 
Rapid cultural changes since the 90s
Traditional customs and practices fading away
Languages evolving or becoming less prominent
Fast fashion replacing slower, more traditional styles
Hip hop and pop music taking precedence over traditional genres
Shift from outdoor play with natural elements to more screen-based activities
Decline in the passing down of stories by grandparents
Decrease in religious adherence among people
Gurdass Maan Saheb put it perfectly.
